            "type": "[fact]",
            "content": "函数$f(x)=a(e^x+a)-x$"
        },
        {
            "id": 2,
            "type": "[intent]",
            "content": "讨论$f(x)$的单调性"
        }
    ],
    "solution": [
        {
            "id": 1001,
            "type": "[knowledge]",
            "content": "分析函数单调性通常需要查看导数的正负"
        },
        {
            "id": 1002,
            "type": "[knowledge]",
            "content": "一个函数的单调增减可以根据导数的正负来确定",
            "ref": 1001
        },
        {
            "id": 1003,
            "type": "[knowledge]",
            "content": "求函数单调性的常用方法是求导数",
            "ref": 1001
        },
        {
            "id": 1004,
            "type": "[knowledge]",
            "content": "指数函数的导数，对于$e^x$，导数是$e^x$"
        },
        {
            "id": 1005,
            "type": "[knowledge]",
            "content": "常数$a$的导数为0"
        },
        {
            "id": 1006,
            "type": "[knowledge]",
            "content": "一次函数$ax$的导数是$a$"
        },
        {
            "id": 1007,
            "type": "[knowledge]",
            "content": "当$a>0$时，函数$a e^{x}$是严格增加的"
        },
        {
            "id": 1008,
            "type": "[knowledge]",
            "content": "函数的二阶导数如果大于0，则函数的一阶导数是增函数"
        },
        {
            "id": 1009,
            "type": "[knowledge]",
            "content": "零点存在定理"
        },
        {
            "id": 3,
            "type": "[reference]",
            "content": "函数$f(x)=a(e^x+a)-x$",
            "ref": 1
        },
        {
            "id": 4,
            "type": "[reference]",
            "content": "分析$f(x)$的单调性",
            "ref": 2
        },
        {
            "id": 5,
            "type": "[fact]",
            "content": "求$f(x)$的一阶导数$f'(x) = ae^x - 1$",
            "dependency": [
                1,
                1003,
                1004,
                1005,
                1006
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6,
            "type": "[fact]",
            "content": "考虑当$a=0$时，$f'(x)=-1<0$",
            "dependency": [
                5
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 7,
            "type": "[fact]",
            "content": "当$a=0$时, $f(x)$单调递减",
            "dependency": [
                6,
                1001
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 8,
            "type": "[fact]",
            "content": "考虑当$a<0$时的$f'(x)$正负",
            "dependency": [
                5
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 9,
            "type": "[fact]",
            "content": "当$a<0$时, $ae^x<0$且$f'(x)<0$",
            "dependency": [
                8,
                1004,
                1005
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 10,
            "type": "[fact]",
            "content": "当$a<0$时, $f(x)$单调递减",
            "dependency": [
                9,
                1001
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 11,
            "type": "[fact]",
            "content": "考虑当$a>0$时的$f'(x)$正负",
            "dependency": [
                5
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 12,
            "type": "[fact]",
            "content": "利用知识经验判断$a>0$时, $ae^x$是增函数，和$f'(x)$的正负变化",
            "dependency": [
                11,
                1007
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 13,
            "type": "[fact]",
            "content": "通过解等式$f'(x)=0$找到零点$x=-\\ln(a)$",
            "dependency": [
                5,
                1009
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 14,
            "type": "[fact]",
            "content": "当$a>0$时，$f(x)$在$(-\\infty,-\\ln(a))$区间单调递减，在$(-\\ln(a),+\\infty)$区间单增",
            "dependency": [
                12,
                13
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 15,
            "type": "[fact]",
            "content": "求二阶导数$f''(x)=ae^x$判断$f'(x)$的增减性",
            "dependency": [
                5,
                1004
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 16,
            "type": "[fact]",
            "content": "当$a>0$时，$f''(x)>0$，因此$f'(x)$是增函数",
            "dependency": [
                15,
                1008
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 17,
            "type": "[fact]",
            "content": "当$a>0$时，可以确定$f'(x)$在$x=-\\ln(a)$处由负变正",
            "dependency": [
                16
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 18,
            "type": "[fact]",
            "content": "$f(x)$的单调性讨论完毕",
            "dependency": [
                7,
                10,
                14
            ]
        }
    ]
